VarAttributes.CATDESC: Proton Flag. Non-zero values indicate that incomplete data was used
VarAttributes.VAR_NOTES: This flag indicates that because of telemetry problems, there was no data for some angular bins.  However, a full pitch angle distribution could be constructed.  Data with nonzero flag should be used with caution.

VarAttributes.VAR_NOTES: Dead time flag.  0: rate<2e5 cts/s, Standard deadtime correction used,. 1: rate>2e5 cts/s.  Use iESA to correct data.
